EXPRESSION: CASE WHEN TRIM(RBF_TJ_1_0.TXN_TIME) = '' THEN to_timestamp(RBF_TJ_1_0.txn_date ||' '||'00:00:00','yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss') ELSE to_timestamp(RBF_TJ_1_0.txn_date || ' '||trim(RBF_TJ_1_0.TXN_TIME),'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss') END
CASE WHEN TRIM(RBF_TJ_1_0.ARDATE) = '' THEN to_date('1000-01-03','yyyy-MM-dd') ELSE COALESCE(to_date(substr(RBF_TJ_1_0.ARDATE,1,8),'yyyyMMDD'),to_date('1000-01-03','yyyy-MM-DD')) END
CASE WHEN TRIM(RBF_TJ_1_0.ARTIME) = '' THEN to_timestamp('00:00:00','HH:mm:ss') ELSE to_timestamp(trim(RBF_TJ_1_0.ARTIME),'HHmmss') END
